txt.en: Many Orcs lurk in Mudmul-charâf, serving no purpose but to endanger the free peoples who roam in Khazad-dûm.
You have defeated several Orcs in their encampment in Mudmul-charâf, making the halls of Zelem-melek safer for travellers to and from the Twenty-first Hall.
Many Orcs lurk in Mudmul-charâf, serving no purpose but to endanger the free peoples who roam in Khazad-dûm.
Orcs can be found in Mudmul-charâf, in the north-west passages of Zelem-melek.\n\nYou should defeat Orcs in Mudmul-charâf.
